OL,3,CVolunteers needed to secure future of
OL,4,C'Holiday for Heroes' scheme
OL,6,FRichard Harwood from the group
OL,7,Fexplains: "They've helped us for a
OL,8,Flong time but there's a possibility
OL,9,Fthey may not always be able to so
OL,10,Fwe're looking for more drivers and
OL,11,Fmore people who have got a military
OL,12,Fbackground and would like to be
OL,13,Finvolved with the charity to help
OL,14,Fthose veterans."
OL,16,FKelly Ganfield from Wiltshire served
OL,17,Fseven years in Northern Ireland
OL,18,Fbetween 1998 and 2005 and lost her
OL,19,Feyesight after suffering two strokes.
